      "comment": "JANIEBQUICK (8) has been good from wider draws on this row in the last two outings, last week working home in good style to finish just 2 metres from the winner in third at Kilmore. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane in play and is she is good enough to take out a race like this. MUSELET (10) drew wide in the last two outings but had put together a string of top-two finishes prior. If things go his way from the back row he can make an impact in this line-up. STAR RULER NZ (6) owns a decent record at this circuit and distance and is in the mix following a fourth at his most recent appearance at Maryborough. MIDNITE DESIRE (4) can feature again after a respectable second at Ararat last time.",
